      "text": "of the Air Force, I have furnished a copy of your",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "letter to that Department for appropriate attention.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "status": "blank"
